HEADWORD: Squaloid
<hw>Squa"loid</hw> <pr>(skw⟦amac⟧"loid)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[NL.
<ets>Squalus</ets> a genus of sharks (fr. L. <ets>squalus</ets> a kind
of sea fish) + <ets>-oid</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Like or
pertaining to a shark or sharks.</def>⟦br⟧
